Package main.com.univlr.commons.utils.statechart

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    StateChartComponent
    An abstract descriptor that represents a component of a state chart.
    StateChartContent
    Represents a state chart content (i.e. a body of a state or transition).
    StateChartFunction
    Represents a function contained in a StateChartComponent.
    StateChartInvariant
    Represents a state chart invariant (i.e. a guard of a state or transition).
    StateChartInvariantAndComponent
    Represents a state chart invariant binary AND component linking two StateChartInvariantComponent.
    StateChartInvariantBinaryComponent
    Represents a state chart invariant binary component linking two StateChartInvariantComponent.
    StateChartInvariantComponent
    Represents a component of a StateChartInvariant of a state chart.
    StateChartInvariantNotComponent
    Represents the negation of a StateChartInvariantComponent of a state chart.
    StateChartInvariantOrComponent
    Represents a state chart invariant binary OR component linking two StateChartInvariantComponent.
    StateChartState
    Represents a state of a state chart.
    StateChartTransition
    Represents a transition to a next state of a state chart.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    StateChartException
    Exception thrown whenever an error occurred on the state chart scope.
    StateChartFunctionException
    Exception thrown whenever an error occurred on the StateChartFunction scope.
    StateChartStateException
    Exception thrown whenever an error occurred on the StateChartState scope.
